After refactoring, the individual panel setters (`setPulseOpen`, `setRelayOpen`, `setMeshOpen`, `setSettingsOpen`, `setPickerOpen`) are no longer needed as hook-level bindings. They can be removed from the top of the hook since `executeUiCommand` accesses them via `useAppStore.getState()`. Keep only what is still needed for non-delegated actions.

